<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4425862>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Parascolopsis akatamae n. sp. (A) and P. eriomma (B–C). A) fresh specimen, OCF-P4098, holotype, 160.5 mm SL, Okinawa-jima Island, Japan; B) fresh specimen, OCF-P4097, 154.4 mm SL, Okinawa-jima Island, Japan; C) preserved specimen, FMNH 52247, holotype, 190.9 mm SL, Kaohsiung, Taiwan." ;
